**ATTESTATION AND ACKNOWLEDGMENT:**

Before me, the undersigned authority, on this Fourteenth Day of March,
1910, personally appeared **Robert Edward Hartley** and **William Samuel
Thoreson**, known to me to be the persons whose names are subscribed to
the foregoing instrument, and acknowledged to me that they executed the
same for the purposes and consideration therein expressed.

Given under my hand and seal of office on the day and year last above
written.

